function tickClock(){const el=$("#clock");if(!el)return;el.textContent=new Date().toLocaleTimeString([],{hour:'2-digit',minute:'2-digit',second:'2-digit'});}
setInterval(tickClock,1000);
let bdayDinged=false,bdayFXon=false;
function celebrateBdayMaybe(){if(bdayDinged||!S.bday)return;const t=new Date();if((+S.bday.split("-")[1]-1)===t.getMonth()&&(+S.bday.split("-")[2])===t.getDate()){bdayDinged=true;setTimeout(birthdayFX,500);}}
function birthdayFX(){
  if(bdayFXon)return;bdayFXon=true;
  const name=S.name?(", "+esc(S.name)):"";
  const ov=document.createElement("div");ov.className="bdayfx";
  ov.innerHTML='<canvas class="bdayfx-cv"></canvas><div class="bdayfx-balloons"></div>'+
    '<div class="bdayfx-banner"><span class="cake">🎂</span><h1>Happy Birthday<span class="nm">'+name+'</span>!</h1><p>Wishing you a year full of discovery.</p><small>tap anywhere to close</small></div>';
  document.body.appendChild(ov);
  ov.addEventListener("click",()=>endFX(ov));
  const bb=ov.querySelector(".bdayfx-balloons"),cols=["#DB4437","#F4B400","#4285F4","#0F9D58","#C77B5A","#9B59B6","#E29AB0"];
  for(let i=0;i<9;i++){const b=document.createElement("div");b.className="bf-balloon";const c=cols[i%cols.length];
    b.style.left=(5+Math.random()*86)+"%";
    b.style.background="radial-gradient(circle at 35% 28%, rgba(255,255,255,.65), "+c+" 46%)";
    b.style.animationDuration=(7.5+Math.random()*4)+"s";b.style.animationDelay=(Math.random()*1.4)+"s";
    b.style.setProperty("--sway",(Math.random()*60-30)+"px");bb.appendChild(b);}
  const cv=ov.querySelector(".bdayfx-cv"),ctx=cv.getContext("2d");let W=cv.width=innerWidth,H=cv.height=innerHeight;
  const colors=["#C7AE7C","#C77B5A","#6E7B4B","#E29AB0","#F4B400","#DB4437","#4285F4","#0F9D58","#FBF7EC","#9B59B6"];
  let parts=[];
  function burst(){for(let i=0;i<180;i++){const a=Math.random()*Math.PI*2,sp=2+Math.random()*9;
    parts.push({x:W*(0.15+Math.random()*0.7),y:H*0.26,vx:Math.cos(a)*sp,vy:Math.sin(a)*sp-5,g:0.13+Math.random()*0.08,w:5+Math.random()*7,h:9+Math.random()*10,rot:Math.random()*6,vr:(Math.random()-.5)*.5,c:colors[i%colors.length],life:0});}}
  burst();setTimeout(burst,700);
  let raf;
  (function frame(){ctx.clearRect(0,0,W,H);for(const p of parts){p.vy+=p.g;p.x+=p.vx;p.y+=p.vy;p.rot+=p.vr;p.life++;
    ctx.save();ctx.translate(p.x,p.y);ctx.rotate(p.rot);ctx.globalAlpha=Math.max(0,1-p.life/250);ctx.fillStyle=p.c;ctx.fillRect(-p.w/2,-p.h/2,p.w,p.h);ctx.restore();}
    parts=parts.filter(p=>p.y<H+40&&p.life<260);raf=requestAnimationFrame(frame);})();
  ov._stop=()=>cancelAnimationFrame(raf);
  try{ding("pop");}catch(e){}
  ov._timer=setTimeout(()=>endFX(ov),6500);
}
function endFX(ov){if(!ov||ov._ended)return;ov._ended=1;clearTimeout(ov._timer);if(ov._stop)ov._stop();ov.classList.add("out");setTimeout(()=>{ov.remove();bdayFXon=false;},500);}
function toggleQ(){S.qOpen=!S.qOpen;save();const c=$(".qotd");if(c){c.classList.toggle("open",S.qOpen);const h=$("#qHint");if(h)h.textContent=S.qOpen?"":"Tap to reveal the answer";}}

function remDateLabel(ds){if(!ds)return"";const p=ds.split("-");const dt=new Date(+p[0],+p[1]-1,+p[2]);return dt.toLocaleDateString('en',{weekday:'short',month:'short',day:'numeric'});}
function notify(title,body,tag){try{if(!('Notification' in window)||Notification.permission!=='granted')return;if(navigator.serviceWorker){navigator.serviceWorker.ready.then(reg=>reg.showNotification(title,{body,icon:"icon-192.png",badge:"icon-192.png",tag:tag||"curio",renotify:true})).catch(()=>{});}else{new Notification(title,{body,icon:"icon-192.png"});}}catch(e){}}
function notifBtnHTML(){if(!('Notification' in window))return '<span class="muted ital" style="font-size:12px">Notifications aren\'t supported on this device</span>';if(Notification.permission==='granted')return '<span class="muted" style="font-size:12px">🔔 Reminder notifications are on</span>';if(Notification.permission==='denied')return '<span class="muted ital" style="font-size:12px">🔕 Notifications are blocked in your browser settings</span>';return '<button class="btn ghost sm" onclick="askNotify()">🔔 Enable reminder notifications</button>';}
function askNotify(){if(!('Notification' in window)){toast('Notifications not supported here');return;}Notification.requestPermission().then(p=>{const el=$('#notifRow');if(el)el.innerHTML=notifBtnHTML();toast(p==='granted'?'Notifications enabled':(p==='denied'?'Notifications blocked':'Maybe later'));if(p==='granted')(S.reminders||[]).forEach(r=>{if(!r.trig)scheduleTrigger(r).then(ok=>{if(ok){r.trig=true;save();}});});});}
function reminderTarget(r){if(!r.time)return null;const tp=r.time.split(":");let target;if(r.date){const dp=r.date.split("-");target=new Date(+dp[0],+dp[1]-1,+dp[2],+tp[0],+tp[1],0,0);}else{target=new Date();target.setHours(+tp[0],+tp[1],0,0);}return new Date(target.getTime()-(r.adv||0)*60000);}
async function scheduleTrigger(r){try{if(!('Notification' in window)||Notification.permission!=='granted')return false;if(typeof TimestampTrigger==='undefined'||!navigator.serviceWorker)return false;const t=reminderTarget(r);if(!t||t.getTime()<=Date.now())return false;const reg=await navigator.serviceWorker.ready;await reg.showNotification("The Living EDIT — "+r.text,{body:"Your almanac reminder"+(r.adv>0?` (in ${r.adv>=60?(r.adv/60)+'h':r.adv+' min'})`:""),icon:"icon-192.png",badge:"icon-192.png",tag:"curio-"+r.id,showTrigger:new TimestampTrigger(t.getTime()),data:{id:r.id}});return true;}catch(e){return false;}}
function drawReminders(){const box=$("#remlist");if(!box)return;
  const list=S.reminders.slice().sort((a,b)=>((a.date||'')+(a.time||'')).localeCompare((b.date||'')+(b.time||'')));
  box.innerHTML=list.length?list.map(r=>{
    const adv=r.adv>0?` · ${r.adv>=60?(r.adv/60)+'h':r.adv+'m'} before`:"";
    const when=[remDateLabel(r.date),r.time||''].filter(Boolean).join(' · ');
    return `<div class="row"><div class="txt">${esc(r.text)}<br><span class="when">${esc(when)}${adv}</span></div>
      <button class="delr" title="Cancel reminder" onclick="delReminder('${r.id}')">✕ Cancel</button></div>`;
  }).join(""):`<div style="color:#bcd0c8;font-style:italic;padding:6px 0">No reminders yet — add one below.</div>`;}
function addReminder(){const text=$("#remText").value.trim();if(!text)return;
  if(!S.reminders)S.reminders=[];
  const r={id:uid(),text,date:$("#remDate").value||isoDate(new Date()),time:$("#remTime").value,adv:parseInt($("#remAdv").value,10)||0};
  S.reminders.push(r);
  save();ding();toast("Reminder set — added to your calendar");$("#remText").value="";drawReminders();refreshCalendar();
  if('Notification' in window){
    if(Notification.permission==='default'){Notification.requestPermission().then(p=>{const el=$('#notifRow');if(el)el.innerHTML=notifBtnHTML();if(p==='granted')scheduleTrigger(r).then(ok=>{if(ok){r.trig=true;save();}});});}
    else if(Notification.permission==='granted'){scheduleTrigger(r).then(ok=>{if(ok){r.trig=true;save();}});}
  }}
function delReminder(id){S.reminders=S.reminders.filter(r=>r.id!==id);save();ding("del");toast("Reminder cancelled");drawReminders();refreshCalendar();
  try{if(navigator.serviceWorker){navigator.serviceWorker.ready.then(reg=>{if(reg.getNotifications)reg.getNotifications({tag:'curio-'+id,includeTriggered:true}).then(ns=>ns.forEach(n=>n.close())).catch(()=>{});}).catch(()=>{});}}catch(e){}}
function calDate(){const t=new Date();return new Date(t.getFullYear(),t.getMonth()+calOffset,1);}
function calStep(delta){calOffset+=delta;refreshCalendar();}
function refreshCalendar(){const b=$("#monthBox");if(b)b.innerHTML=monthCardHTML(calDate());}
function checkReminders(){const now=new Date();S.reminders.forEach(r=>{
  if(!r.time)return;const tp=r.time.split(":");
  let target;if(r.date){const dp=r.date.split("-");target=new Date(+dp[0],+dp[1]-1,+dp[2],+tp[0],+tp[1],0,0);}else{target=new Date();target.setHours(+tp[0],+tp[1],0,0);}
  target=new Date(target.getTime()-(r.adv||0)*60000);
  const diff=now-target;if(diff>=0&&diff<60000&&!firedRem[r.id]){firedRem[r.id]=1;popReminder(r);}});}
function popReminder(r){$("#rpText").textContent=r.text+(r.adv>0?` (in ${r.adv>=60?(r.adv/60)+'h':r.adv+' min'})`:"");$("#rempop").classList.add("show");ding("pop");if(!r.trig)notify("The Living EDIT — "+r.text,"Your almanac reminder","curio-"+r.id);}
function closePop(){$("#rempop").classList.remove("show");}
setInterval(checkReminders,20000);

